st &eacute;gale ou inf&eacute;rieur au Points de Magie de Glaaki (28) moins les Points de Magie du sorcier)</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":true,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":false,"gate":false,"combat":false},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"qt7WXtn9nMyMtrNI"}
